    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride, and she's been absolutely wonderful to me. It's in really solid shape and drives like a dream\u2014perfect for your daily commute or a fun weekend road trip! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin!",
