    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist\u2019s specimen featuring the S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 with its signature 8,400 RPM redline. The engine's individual throttle bodies offer razor-sharp response, while the M Variable Differential Lock ensures optimal power distribution across the rear axle. The chassis retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity, complemented by a dual-clutch transmission that executes rev-matched downshifts with precision. Recent preventative maintenance on the rod bearings and throttle actuators ensures the valvetrain and VANOS systems are performing at peak efficiency. A mechanically sound example of high-revving engineering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained. Ready for immediate sale.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
