      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really great shape and has been super reliable for everything from daily commutes to fun weekend getaways. Everything runs nice and smooth, and the interior is still looking super clean and cozy. It\u2019s a fantastic car that\u2019s ready to hit the road with its next owner! I\u2019d love for you to come by, check it out, and take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
