      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The engine retains excellent compression, and the VANOS unit has been professionally overhauled to ensure precise variable valve timing. Power is managed through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. The chassis remains rigid, with documented subframe reinforcement already completed\u2014a critical upgrade for this platform. Suspension components feature refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, maintaining the car's neutral handling characteristics and sharp turn-in. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the mechanical drivetrain and cooling system are robust and track-ready.",
      "price": 29500.0,
